sentences.sentence: Piping erection work include: prefabrication, placing, aligning, welding and bolting.

sentences.sentence: The project proved to be a best-case scenario for illustrating the efficiencies of prefabrication.

sentences.sentence: Prefabrication: Assembly of standardized Building components at a location other than the Building site.
sentences.translation: 预制：预制是指标准建筑构件在其它地点而不是在建筑所处的最终位置上进行的装配。
